Class Curve.PrimitivesBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • mloss.roc.Curve.Builder<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Integer>
      • mloss.roc.Curve.PrimitivesBuilder
  • Enclosing class:
    Curve

    public static class Curve.PrimitivesBuilder
extends Curve.Builder<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Integer>

    This class is the same as Curve.Builder except this takes arrays of primitives as input (instead of sequences of objects). Scores must be doubles and labels must be integers. (Labels must compare exactly.) The default positive label is 1.

    All arrays of primitives are converted to lists of number objects.
